text: I think you should write her love notes. It will make her so happy she'll have to live longer.
There is a lack of kindness in the world. Not knowing someone isn't a good reason not to help them and that seems to be our excuse everyday.

The world really is a beautiful place, don't let anyone ruin that for you.
I'm feeling so much better about my writing. There is so much inspiration around me right now.
